Detailed Description

template<typename T = double>
class geometry::latitude< T >

Class to construct point_ll with latitude value (north/south).

Template parameters:
  • T coordinate type, double / float, should correspond to point_ll type
Note:
Often combined with dms class
Examples:

2_point_ll_example.cpp, and 5_distance_example.cpp.
